						 <p>I like it. As someone who's played GTA 5/Online for like three years now, I like it a real lot.</p> <p>I just wanted to point out that the computer OS system for Apple in GTA is Fruit, not iFruit. Kinda like how iOS and OSX are like, almost the same in the name.</p> <p>EDIT: Also Trevor does meth, not cocaine. He's like straight edge like that. Very unhinged dude.</p> 
				 	]]>
